<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

  <%- include("../shared/head", { pageTitle: "Orbit | Pricing" }) %>

  <body>

    <%- include("../shared/header") %>

    <main class="container page-panel marketing-page marketing-page--pricing">

      <p class="marketing-eyebrow marketing-eyebrow--pricing-cards">Pricing</p>

      <header class="marketing-hero marketing-hero--pricing-top">

        <h1>Explorer and Pro</h1>

        <p class="marketing-lead">

          <strong>Explorer</strong> is free: full tracker and assistant on a compact model.

          <strong>Pro</strong> is paid: same product with heavier models and persistent chat history.

          Details are in the cards below.

        </p>

      </header>

      <section class="marketing-pricing-grid marketing-pricing-grid--top" aria-label="Plans and actions">

        <article class="marketing-price-card">

          <h2>Explorer</h2>

          <p class="marketing-price">Free</p>

          <p>Start with the full tracker and the compact-model assistant—no card required.</p>

          <ul class="marketing-list">

            <li>Mission-style agent on an efficient model</li>

            <li>Rate limits aimed at individual exploration</li>

            <li>Upgrade anytime if you outgrow “quick answers”</li>

          </ul>

          <a href="/signup" class="button button-secondary">Get started</a>

        </article>



        <article class="marketing-price-card marketing-price-card--featured">

          <h2>Pro</h2>

          <p class="marketing-price">$7 <span class="marketing-price-period">/ month</span></p>

          <p>Frontier models, stronger reasoning, and persistent history for serious flight and ops analysis.</p>

          <ul class="marketing-list">

            <li>Pro model access in the same agent panel (fair-use per month at launch)</li>

            <li><strong>Persistent chat history</strong> across sessions, tied to your flights</li>

            <li>Room for longer investigations before you hit limits</li>

          </ul>

          <a href="/contact" class="button button-primary">Purchase</a>

        </article>

        <!--

          Future: third pricing column (e.g. token / usage add-on or enterprise).

          Grid already uses auto-fit; drop another <article class="marketing-price-card"> here.

        -->

      </section>

    </main>

  </body>

</html>

